com.ibm.disni.rdma.verbs

类 IbvCQ

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.disni.rdma.verbs.IbvCQ
  • 直接已知子类:
    NatIbvCQ

    public class IbvCQ
extends Object
    Represents a completion queue. IOCompletion queues hold events indicated the completion of data transfer operations. Several queue pairs (QPs) can share the same completion queue.
